# 

 
 # 题目背景 
<p>noip2016提高组试题&nbsp;官方数据</p> 

 
 # 题目描述 
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">小c同学认为跑步非常有趣,于是决定制作一款叫做《天天爱跑步》的游戏。&laquo;天天爱跑步&raquo;是一个养成类游戏,需要玩家每天按时上线,完成打卡任务。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">这个游戏的地图可以看作一一棵包含&nbsp;<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_bg==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />个结点和&nbsp;<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_bi0x.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />条边的树,&nbsp;每条边连接两个结点,且任意两个结点存在一条路径互相可达。树上结点编号为从<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_MQ==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />到<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_bg==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />的连续正整数。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">现在有<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_bQ==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />个玩家,第<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_aQ==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />个玩家的起点为&nbsp;<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_U19p.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />,终点为&nbsp;<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_VF9p.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />&nbsp;。每天打卡任务开始时,所有玩家在第<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_MA==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />秒同时从自己的起点出发,&nbsp;以每秒跑一条边的速度,&nbsp;不间断地沿着最短路径向着自己的终点跑去,&nbsp;跑到终点后该玩家就算完成了打卡任务。&nbsp;(由于地图是一棵树,&nbsp;所以每个人的路径是唯一的)</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">小C想知道游戏的活跃度,&nbsp;所以在每个结点上都放置了一个观察员。&nbsp;在结点<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_ag==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />的观察员会选择在第<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_V19q.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />秒观察玩家,&nbsp;一个玩家能被这个观察员观察到当且仅当该玩家在第<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_V19q.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />秒也理到达了结点&nbsp;<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_ag==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />&nbsp;。&nbsp;小C想知道每个观察员会观察到多少人?</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">注意:&nbsp;我们认为一个玩家到达自己的终点后该玩家就会结束游戏,&nbsp;他不能等待一&nbsp;段时间后再被观察员观察到。&nbsp;即对于把结点<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_ag==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />作为终点的玩家:&nbsp;若他在第<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_V19q.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />秒重到达终点,则在结点<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_ag==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />的观察员不能观察到该玩家;若他正好在第<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_V19q.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />秒到达终点,则在结点<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_ag==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />的观察员可以观察到这个玩家。</p> 

 
 # 输入格式 
<p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(81, 81, 81); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">输入格式：</span></p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">第一行有两个整数<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_bg==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />和<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_bQ==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />&nbsp;。其中<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_bg==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />代表树的结点数量,&nbsp;同时也是观察员的数量,&nbsp;<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_bQ==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />代表玩家的数量。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">接下来&nbsp;<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_bi0lMjAx.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />行每行两个整数<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_dQ==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />和&nbsp;<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_dg==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />,表示结点&nbsp;<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_dQ==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />到结点&nbsp;<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_dg==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />有一条边。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">接下来一行&nbsp;<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_bg==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />个整数,其中第<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_ag==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />个整数为<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_V19q.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />&nbsp;,&nbsp;表示结点<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_ag==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />出现观察员的时间。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">接下来&nbsp;<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_bQ==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />行,每行两个整数<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_U19p.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />,和<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_VF9p.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />,表示一个玩家的起点和终点。</p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.6rem 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">对于所有的数据,保证<img src="/source/joyoi/tyvj-4759/img/aHR0cDovL2xhdGV4LmNvZGVjb2dzLmNvbS9naWYubGF0ZXg_MVxsZXElMjBTX2ksVF9pXGxlcSUyMG4sJTIwMFxsZXElMjBXX2pcbGVxJTIwbg==.latex" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" />&nbsp;。</p>
